      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is ideal for someone looking for a project car or a source of spare parts. The engine currently has significant mechanical issues and does not run, and the body shows noticeable rust and several dents. The interior has seen better days, with significant tearing in the upholstery and a non-functional dashboard. Please be aware that this car will need to be towed and requires extensive restoration or mechanical expertise to return to the road.",
